<br>
Could use em with the Fighting Baton (No plusses to anything) or with a Polished Steel Ulak (Bunch of plusses as well as 25 hps).<br>
<br>
Then should I use KD in the offhand or in the mainhand.<br>
<br>
Level 25 if that matters.<br>
<br>
Thanks in advance. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukasekill2.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kasekill2</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(7/4/02 7:31:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1666.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Weapon Choices</span><hr size=1> I prefer to put a faster weapon in my primary hand.  I am level 43 and I use a FB in primary and KD in secondary, but you may want to use KD in primary since you don't get as much DMG bonus yet.  FB has a little better ratio than the PSU, but with the stats I think they pretty much even out.  <br>
<br>
IMO, I would get an FB.  At your level I would put KD prime and FB in secondary once you start getting more DMG bonus I would switch them around. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uroyceli.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Royceli</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(7/4/02 12:20:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1666.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Weapon Choices</span><hr size=1> Since you do not get any dmg bonus to your primary hand yet (not until lvl 28 ), it's usually best to use the best ratio weapon in your primary hand.  KDs are 14/28 which is a 2 ratio.  FBs would be 8/20 = 2.5 and PSU is 9/27 = 3.  Another weapon which may be in your price range is a Cane of Tranquil which is 11/25 = 2.2.  I would probably use the KDs in primary and either a CoT or an FB in your offhand.  By the time one of the other weapons will outdamage the slower KD in primary due to the dmg bonus, you will probably be at a point where you can afford a better one, like the Jade Mace 9/18.<br>
<br>
It's also a good idea to practice all types of weapons (1H Blunt, 2H Blunt and Hand2Hand) at this stage so you won't have to play catch up on your skills later.  If you can afford a PSU, grab one and use it to work on your H2H skills too.  Also, the bamboo bo stick (8/20) is a nice little 2h blunt weapon to practice skills.  It's not very useful for dmg, but can be used in group situations or to beat on a fleeing mob. <p>Royceli, Lvl 51 Human Monk <BR>
The Nameless <BR>
<A HREF=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=218251>My Slim Gear (Cuz it ain't Phat)</A></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usolarise.showPublicProfile?language=EN>solarise</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 41<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(7/4/02 4:46:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1666.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> agree</span><hr size=1> /agree royceli, good to train all skills, and suggestions are on some decent items that are also decently priced.  if you can't get the PSU, you can always use fists.  i would use the KD main, FB off if pure dps, and remember to train your 2hb also, to train h2h, i would prolly do PSU/KD, will train faster since you swing more w/ your main hand, and swinging w/ offhand % is not that high, so i opt for the dmg, heh heh, good luck <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showPrevMessage?topicID=1666.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showNextMessage?topicID=1666.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1666.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.emailToFriend?topicID=1666.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybus